genresAdvancedInfo.name: zomi pop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Zomi pop is a genre of music that originated in Myanmar and is characterized by its fusion of traditional Zomi music with contemporary pop and rock elements. It often features soaring vocals, intricate guitar work, and catchy hooks, and is popular throughout Southeast Asia.
